Khartoum â€” The Assistant of the President of the Republic, the Deputy Chairman for the National Congress for Party Affairs, Dr. Faisal Hassan Ibrahim has affirmed the importance for ending peace and war issue in South Kordofan and the contribution of all sectors in this connection. This came when Dr. Faisal received, Wednesday, a delegation representing the leaderships of the State of South Kordofan. Dr. Faisal welcomed the delegation, confirming that peace represents basic option of the state and referring to the cease-fire which announced many times by the President of the Republic. He called on all sectors to contribute to the realization of pace and ending the war in the area.